verbose_text: Skeletal muscle expression of the following genes was studied : complement component C3 (C3), tissue-type plasminogen activator (PLAT), human forkhead-box C2 gene (FOXC2), nuclear factor kappa B (NFKB1), inhibitor of nuclear factor kappa B kinase beta subunit (IKBKB), hypoxia inducible factor 1, alpha subunit (HIF1alpha), IL6, heme-oxygenase-1 (HMOX1), endothelial nitric oxide synthase (NOS3), heat shock 70 kDa protein (HSPA1A), Cu/Zn-superoxide dismutase (SOD1), and glutathione peroxidase (GPX1).
